<paragraph blockId="3.[111,648,818,1700]" box="[113,210,818,844]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[111,648,818,1700]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
<bibRefCitation author="CANDOLLE A. P. DE" box="[113,347,849,876]" firstAuthor="De Candolle" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref9290" refString="CANDOLLE A. P. DE. 1837. - Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis. Vol. VI. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Paris, 687 p." type="book" year="1837">De Candolle (1837)</bibRefCitation>
included 
<taxonomicName box="[465,595,850,876]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="canescens">
<emphasis box="[465,595,850,876]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. canescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[116,216,881,907]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="viscosa">
<emphasis box="[116,216,881,907]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. viscosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
into the circumscription of the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[113,250,913,939]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[113,216,913,939]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Santolina</emphasis>
L.
</taxonomicName>
, and reduced 
<taxonomicName authority="Lag." authorityName="Lag." box="[412,596,913,939]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[412,539,913,939]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
Lag.
</taxonomicName>
as a variety of 
<taxonomicName authority="Benth." authorityName="Benth." box="[218,413,944,971]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[218,336,945,971]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
Benth.
</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis box="[426,548,944,970]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">nom. illegit.</emphasis>
). The author retained the epithet “ 
<taxonomicName box="[387,481,977,1002]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[387,481,977,1002]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">pectinata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” for a variety 
<emphasis box="[626,639,978,1005]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">α</emphasis>
, whereas he conserved the 
<typeStatus box="[391,437,1008,1034]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="Lag." authorityName="Lag." box="[472,647,1008,1034]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[472,593,1008,1034]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
Lag.
</taxonomicName>
for a variety 
<emphasis box="[256,269,1042,1069]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β</emphasis>
. He published var. 
<emphasis box="[491,504,1042,1069]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[521,646,1039,1065]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[521,646,1039,1065]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on plants from the 
<emphasis box="[389,527,1071,1097]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">locus classicus</emphasis>
of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. He also cited 
<taxonomicName authority="Lag." authorityName="Lag." box="[321,496,1103,1129]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[321,442,1103,1129]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
Lag.
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of this name, adding a short note as diagnosis “ 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">foliis infimis et junioribus linearibus indivisis margine tuberculatis</emphasis>
”. 
<taxonomicName authority="Benth." authorityName="Benth." box="[258,540,1198,1224]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[258,458,1198,1224]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Santolina pectinata</emphasis>
Benth.
</taxonomicName>
, non 
<taxonomicName authority="DC." authorityName="DC." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
Lag. var. 
<emphasis box="[157,170,1232,1259]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[182,306,1229,1255]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">heterophylla</emphasis>
DC.
</taxonomicName>
, is an invalid name(ICBN: arts 53.1, 26.2; 
<bibRefCitation author="Mcneill" box="[292,501,1261,1288]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Mcneill" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref9601" refString="MCNEILL J., BARRIE F. R., BURDET H. M., DE- MOULIN V., HAWKSWORTH D. L., MARHOLD K., NICOLSON D. H., PRADO J., SILVA P. C., SKOG J. E., WIERSEMA J. H. &amp; TURLAND N. J. 2006. - International Code of Botanical Nomenclature (Vienna Code) adopted by the Seventeenth International Botanical Congress Vienna. Austria, July 2005. A. R." type="proceedings" year="2006">
Mcneill 
<emphasis box="[382,425,1261,1287]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">et al</emphasis>
. 2006
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[111,648,818,1700]" lastBlockId="3.[674,1212,216,1699]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
Furthermore,Willkomm &amp; Cutanda 
<emphasis box="[509,530,1294,1319]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">in</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Willkomm" firstAuthor="Willkomm" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" pagination="106 - 107" refId="ref9993" refString="WILLKOMM M. 1859. - Pugillus plantarum novarum peninsulae pyrenaicae. Linnaea 30: 106 - 107." type="journal article" year="1859">Willkomm (1859)</bibRefCitation>
, and Willkomm 
<emphasis box="[386,408,1325,1350]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">in</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Willkomm &amp; Lange" firstAuthor="Willkomm" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref10035" refString="WILLKOMM M. &amp; LANGE J. 1865. - Prodromus Florae Hispanicae II. Typis e sumtibus librariae E. Schweizerbart, Stuttgartiae, 680 p." type="book" year="1865">Willkomm &amp; Lange (1865)</bibRefCitation>
ignored the variety 
<taxonomicName box="[393,538,1356,1385]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[393,404,1358,1385]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[416,538,1356,1382]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
published by 
<bibRefCitation author="CANDOLLE A. P. DE" box="[143,362,1388,1415]" firstAuthor="De Candolle" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref9290" refString="CANDOLLE A. P. DE. 1837. - Prodromus systematis naturalis regni vegetabilis. Vol. VI. Sumptibus Sociorum Treuttel et Wurtz, Paris, 687 p." type="book" year="1837">De Candolle (1837)</bibRefCitation>
. Willkomm &amp; Cutanda 
<emphasis box="[623,645,1389,1414]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">in</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Willkomm" box="[112,305,1419,1446]" firstAuthor="Willkomm" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" pagination="106 - 107" refId="ref9993" refString="WILLKOMM M. 1859. - Pugillus plantarum novarum peninsulae pyrenaicae. Linnaea 30: 106 - 107." type="journal article" year="1859">Willkomm (1859)</bibRefCitation>
published a new taxon, 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, based on a specimen from Sierra de Gredos. Willkomm 
<emphasis box="[235,257,1484,1509]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">in</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Willkomm &amp; Lange" box="[261,555,1483,1510]" firstAuthor="Willkomm" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref10035" refString="WILLKOMM M. &amp; LANGE J. 1865. - Prodromus Florae Hispanicae II. Typis e sumtibus librariae E. Schweizerbart, Stuttgartiae, 680 p." type="book" year="1865">Willkomm &amp; Lange (1865)</bibRefCitation>
reduced 
<taxonomicName authority="Wilk. &amp; Cut." authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" box="[112,417,1515,1541]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[112,263,1515,1541]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. heterophylla</emphasis>
Wilk. &amp; Cut.
</taxonomicName>
to a variety of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifolia">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but he omitted Cutanda as author of the epithet. He cited 
<taxonomicName authority="Lag." authorityName="Lag." box="[334,503,1578,1605]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[334,452,1578,1604]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
Lag.
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of “ 
<emphasis box="[154,238,1610,1636]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">variat 1</emphasis>
” of 
<taxonomicName authority="Willk." authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifolia">
<emphasis box="[289,464,1610,1636]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
L. var. 
<emphasis box="[552,565,1612,1639]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β</emphasis>
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">heterophylla</emphasis>
Willk.
</taxonomicName>
, whereas 
<bibRefCitation author="Willkomm" box="[352,551,1641,1668]" firstAuthor="Willkomm" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref10012" refString="WILLKOMM M. 1893. - Supplementum Prodromi Florae Hispanicae. Schweizerbart (E. Koch), Stuttgartiae, 370 p." type="book" year="1893">Willkomm (1893)</bibRefCitation>
changed the original concept and accepted 
<taxonomicName authority="Willk." authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" box="[475,948,216,1700]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifolia">
<emphasis box="[475,488,1673,1699]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[500,646,1673,1699]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[723,736,218,245]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β</emphasis>
<emphasis box="[745,869,216,242]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">heterophylla</emphasis>
Willk.
</taxonomicName>
, f. 
<emphasis box="[983,997,216,242]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">1</emphasis>
Willk. as synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[707,832,248,274]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[707,720,248,274]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[737,832,248,273]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">pectinata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. He placed this 
<emphasis box="[1017,1080,248,273]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">variat</emphasis>
in the 
<typeStatus box="[1163,1209,248,274]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">type</typeStatus>
locality of 
<taxonomicName box="[797,923,280,306]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pectinata">
<emphasis box="[797,923,280,306]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. pectinata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and in Sierra de la Sagra (COI-WILLK 00035964, MPU, P 00752621 from “La Puebla de Don Fadrique et montem La Sagra”).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[674,1212,216,1699]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
Willkomm misspelled the locality for the 
<typeStatus box="[1115,1208,374,400]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" box="[704,855,406,432]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[704,855,406,432]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; the correct name is “Serranillos” (
<bibRefCitation author="Cerveira Rodrigues Gomes" box="[684,1046,437,464]" firstAuthor="Cerveira Rodrigues Gomes" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" refId="ref9387" refString="CERVEIRA RODRIGUES GOMES C. I. 2000. - Estudo nomenclatural e taxonomico de ejemplares tipo do herbario de Willkomm. Universidade de Coimbra, Departamento de Botanica. Jardim Botanico, Coimbra." type="book" year="2000">Cerveira Rodrigues Gomes 2000</bibRefCitation>
), and it will be used hereafter in this paper.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[674,1212,216,1699]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
Two collections of Isern were found. In the first one, labelled with the name “ 
<taxonomicName box="[986,1133,532,559]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis box="[986,1133,532,559]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. oblongifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, from Puerto del Pico (
<accessionNumber box="[845,980,564,591]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/MA126799" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">MA 126799</accessionNumber>
), the date is only indicated as“August”.The other specimen (COI-WILLK 00035956), labelled by Willkomm with the names 
<taxonomicName box="[675,967,659,688]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis box="[675,967,659,688]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. oblongifolia β ceratophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" box="[1017,1166,659,686]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[1017,1166,659,686]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was gathered by Isern in 
<date box="[890,993,691,718]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" value="1855-07">
July 
<quantity box="[937,993,691,718]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.7116999999999996" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" unit="in" value="1855.0">1855</quantity>
</date>
in Sierra de Gredos. Presumably, Willkomm changed 1855 into 1857 during transcription of the original label.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[674,1212,216,1699]" lastBlockId="5.[111,649,216,1193]" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="138" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">
The 
<typeStatus box="[748,844,786,812]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">lectotype</typeStatus>
(COI-WILLK 00035956; 
<figureCitation box="[1138,1202,786,812]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="4.[351,362,1680,1697]" captionTargetBox="[160,1163,215,1629]" captionTargetId="figure-26@4.[160,1163,215,1629]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIG 2. — Lectotype of Santolina heterophylla Willk. (COI-WILLK 00035956)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5205805" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5205805/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
) has six flowering stems and various sterile stems. The sheet has two labels in the centre of the lower margin with the following notation in black ink: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[678,758,913,939]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Label 1</emphasis>
: “Herbarium Willkommi [printed] // 
<taxonomicName authority="Mill." authorityName="Mill." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifolia">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Santolina rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
Mill.
</taxonomicName>
[underlined] var?. 
<taxonomicName box="[1145,1209,945,970]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sericea">
<emphasis box="[1145,1209,945,970]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">sericea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[underlined] Wk.= 
<taxonomicName authority="Wk." authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" box="[881,1075,976,1003]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[881,1024,976,1003]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. heterophylla</emphasis>
Wk.
</taxonomicName>
[underlined] et Cut. // Sierra de Gredos [Willkomm’s handwritten notation] // Legit [printed] Ysern // 
<date box="[1098,1209,1039,1066]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" value="1855-07">Julio 1855</date>
[Willkomm’s handwritten notation]”; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1064,1141,1071,1097]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Label 2</emphasis>
: “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boiss." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Santolina oblongifolia</emphasis>
Boiss.
</taxonomicName>
[underlined] 
<emphasis box="[1072,1210,1103,1132]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">β ceratophylla</emphasis>
[underlined] Wk. [Willkomm’s handwritten notation]”. This specimen has two revision labels by D. Sánchez-Mata and S. Sardinero with the following notation in black ink: 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[903,981,1229,1256]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Label 1</emphasis>
: “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Willk." authorityName="Willk. (Willkomm &amp; Lange" authorityYear="1865" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="oblongifolia" variety="ceratophylla">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Santolina oblongifolia</emphasis>
Boiss var. 
<emphasis box="[815,934,1261,1287]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">ceratophylla</emphasis>
Willk.
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis box="[1014,1036,1262,1287]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">in</emphasis>
Willk. &amp; Lange // Typus [handwritten] // 
<collectingRegion box="[950,1045,1293,1319]" country="Portugal" name="Coimbra" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Coimbra</collectingRegion>
[printed] 
<date pageId="3" pageNumber="136" value="1993-09">1993 IX</date>
[handwritten]”; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[882,962,1324,1351]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Label 2</emphasis>
: “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boiss." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis box="[987,1210,1324,1350]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Santolina oblongifolia</emphasis>
Boiss.
</taxonomicName>
[handwritten] // 
<collectingRegion box="[920,1015,1356,1382]" country="Portugal" name="Coimbra" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Coimbra</collectingRegion>
[printed] 
<date box="[1121,1209,1356,1383]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" value="1993-09">1993 IX</date>
[handwritten]”. This specimen displays all the characteristics listed in the protologue (Appendix 1). The 
<typeStatus box="[677,772,1451,1477]" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">lectotype</typeStatus>
clearly shows intermediate characteristics between 
<taxonomicName box="[770,915,1483,1510]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis box="[770,783,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[797,915,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">oblongifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="subsp. rosmarinifolia" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="rosmarinifolia" subSpecies="rosmarinifolia">
<emphasis box="[968,981,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[995,1137,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis box="[677,820,1515,1541]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The relationship between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="subsp. rosmarinifolia" box="[755,1160,1546,1573]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="rosmarinifolia" subSpecies="rosmarinifolia">
<emphasis box="[755,930,1546,1573]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis box="[1014,1160,1546,1572]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">rosmarinifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[678,823,1578,1604]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
<emphasis box="[678,823,1578,1604]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">S. oblongifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been cited by 
<bibRefCitation author="Willkomm" box="[1015,1211,1578,1605]" firstAuthor="Willkomm" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" pagination="106 - 107" refId="ref9993" refString="WILLKOMM M. 1859. - Pugillus plantarum novarum peninsulae pyrenaicae. Linnaea 30: 106 - 107." type="journal article" year="1859">Willkomm (1859)</bibRefCitation>
in the protologue: “ 
<emphasis box="[876,1024,1610,1636]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Specie proxima</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Mill." authorityName="Mill." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="136" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifoliae">
S. rosmarinifoliae 
<emphasis box="[677,731,1641,1667]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">Mill.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis italics="true" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="138" pageId="3" pageNumber="136">, a cujus formis numerosis foliis eximie heteromorphis planis sericeis statim distinguitur. Calathiorum florumque structura a</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[345,521,216,242]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="5" pageNumber="138" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosmarinifolia">S. rosmarinifolia</taxonomicName>
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">non differre videtur, sed propter foliorum formam ab omnibus</emphasis>
Santolinis 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">valde discrepantem hanc stirpem ad illam speciem referre non audeo.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boiss." box="[379,594,311,337]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="5" pageNumber="138" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="oblongifolia">
S. oblongifolia 
<emphasis box="[538,594,312,337]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">Boiss.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">foliis planis sericeis pariter gaudens ramis sterilibus elongatis, foliis multo minus difformibus aliaque ratione formatis a nostra differre videtur</emphasis>
[
<emphasis box="[364,392,407,432]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">…</emphasis>
]”.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5205805" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5205805" box="[351,974,1680,1697]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5205805/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="137" startId="4.[351,362,1680,1697]" targetBox="[160,1163,215,1629]" targetPageId="4">
<paragraph blockId="4.[351,974,1680,1697]" box="[351,974,1680,1697]" pageId="4" pageNumber="137">
FIG 2. — Lectotype of 
<taxonomicName authority="Willk." authorityName="Willk. &amp; Cut. (Willkomm" authorityYear="1859" box="[535,771,1680,1697]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Santolina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[535,719,1680,1697]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="137">Santolina heterophylla</emphasis>
Willk.
